a futuristic robotic mecha praciticing boxing punch, it have a silver armor body with lightning energy surrounding the robotic body. Every punch from the mecha showing lightning effect projected on the gloves.

The futuristic robotic mecha, as towering figure clad in sleek, metallic armor stands defiantly against a stormy sky, their form bathed in the crackling energy of lightning. The suit is intricately designed, with sharp lines and glowing red accents that pulse with power. A flowing crimson cape billows behind them, catching the wind as they grip a high-tech device in one hand—a compact yet formidable weapon emitting faint blue light. Their helmet features angular wings that seem to channel the raw electricity surging around them, while intricate circuits and mechanical details on the armor hint at advanced technology fused with sheer strength.
